 </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"bfw-section\" id=\"bloomli-approach\">\n    <div class=\"bfw-container\">\n      <div class=\"bfw-centered\">\n        <p class=\"bfw-eyebrow\">Beauty From Within</p>\n        <h2>A softer approach to hair, beauty, and women’s wellness.</h2>\n        <p>\n          We believe beauty is not just one product, one step, or one quick fix. It is a routine — the small things you do consistently to feel more confident, cared for, and like yourself.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bfw-cards\">\n        <div class=\"bfw-card\">\n          <div class=\"bfw-icon\">✦</div>\n          <h3>Nourish from within</h3>\n          <p>\n            Our supplements are designed to support your beauty routine from the inside out with daily formats that fit different lifestyles.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"bfw-card\">\n          <div class=\"bfw-icon\">♡</div>\n          <h3>Care on the outside</h3>\n          <p>\n            Our hair care products are made to complement your routine with simple, nourishing steps that feel beautiful to use.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"bfw-card\">\n          <div class=\"bfw-icon\">☼</div>\n          <h3>Make consistency easy</h3>\n          <p>\n            Beauty support works best when it becomes part of your life. Bloomli is built to make that routine feel simple, pretty, and realistic.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"bfw-section bfw-soft\">\n    <div class=\"bfw-container bfw-split\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"bfw-eyebrow\">Our Mission</p>\n        <h2>Helping women feel more confident in their daily beauty routine.</h2>\n\n        <p>\n          Hair and beauty can feel emotional. Some days your routine feels effortless, and other days it feels like nothing is working. Bloomli exists to make beauty care feel less complicated 